 vnd <instruction>tuee <ingredient en="spice" commodity="Q42527">gewurcz</ingredient> daran</instruction>
 <instruction>zu dem <ingredient en="head" commodity="Q23640">haubt</ingredient> nym ein virdunng <ingredient en="grape" commodity="Q10978">weinper</ingredient> vnd ain virdung <ingredient en="almond" commodity="Q184357">mandel</ingredient></instruction>
 <instruction>die schell schon</instruction>
 <instruction>stozz die <ingredient en="grape" commodity="Q10978">weinper</ingredient> vnd die <ingredient en="almond" commodity="Q184357">mandel</ingredient> durch einander</instruction>
 <ab n="1" type="recipe" subtype="subrecipe" xml:lang="de-x-enh" xml:id="b4.15.sub.1"><opener>Wildu <title key="Southern wine sauce">ein gutte <dish en="sauce" commodity="Q178359">Salssen</dish></title> haben</opener> <instruction>die solt du <alternative reason="ingredient">mit <pb xml:id="B4_075r" n="075r"/> <ingredient commodity="Q107262739" en="rainval">Rayffall</ingredient> Oder mit <ingredient commodity="Q107262741" en="rumanier">Ruemannyer</ingredient></alternative> durchslachen</instruction>
 <instruction>do tuee ein guet <ingredient en="spice" commodity="Q42527">gewuercz</ingredient> an vnd <ingredient en="unrefined cane sugar" commodity="Q57656231">zukcher</ingredient></instruction>
 <closer>so hastu ein gutte <dish en="sauce" commodity="Q178359">salssen</dish></closer></ab> </div></body></text></TEI>